text: "Do Ya" is a 1972 song by British band The Move and was more popular when Electric Light Orchestra covered it for their sixth studio album A New World Record. It went to number 13 in Canada. ==Electric Light Orchestra version== ==References== Category:1972 songs Category:1977 songs Category:Electric Light Orchestra songs Category:Todd Rundgren songs Category:Glam rock songs Category:Power pop songs
